Template: custom-conf-mysql/bind-address
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Bind to a specific address ?
 Please specify which address to bind the service to:
 .
  - {empty}:   do not bind to any specific address (security risk)
  - localhost: bind to the localhost address (private service)
  - gateway:   bind to the address matching configured gateway/network
  - <addr>:    actual IP address

Template: custom-conf-mysql/ssl-enable
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Enable SSL/TLS (requires valid certificate) ?

